# Screenshots

This folder contains the main UI screenshots and workflow demonstrations for Team Nexus.

Team Nexus is a real-time collaboration platform designed for team communication, task management, shared workspaces, and file collaboration.

---

## Included Screens

### Workspace Dashboard
Shows all available workspaces and allows users to create and manage collaborative spaces.

![Workspace Dashboard](./workspace-dashboard.png)

---

### Kanban Task Board
Kanban-style workflow management with task status tracking and drag-and-drop style organization.

![Kanban Board](./kanban-board.png)

---

### Task List
Displays personal tasks with due dates, start dates, and task sources.

![Task List](./task-list.png)

---

### Task Detail Modal
Detailed task editing interface with assignee management, scheduling, and task descriptions.

![Task Detail Modal](./task-detail-modal.png)

---

### Shared Files
Shared team file management and upload functionality for collaborative workspaces.

![Shared Files](./shared-files.png)

---

### Notifications
Notification center for updates and collaboration events.

![Notifications](./notifications-page.png)

---

### Team Chat
Built-in team messaging and communication interface.

![Chat Page](./chat-page.png)

---
